sourcesContent: import React from "react"; import { Typography, Box, Button, Container, Grid, Card, CardContent } from "@mui/material"; import { useInView } from "react-intersection-observer"; import "./HomePage.css"; // Add a CSS file for custom animations const HomePage = () => { const { ref: paragraphRef, inView: paragraphInView } = useInView({ triggerOnce: true, threshold: 0.2, }); return ( {/* Hero Section */} Welcome to CautisCloud {/* Project Description Section */} About CautisCloud CautisCloud is an innovative decentralized cloud storage platform that ensures security, privacy, and reliability. Files are split into chunks, distributed across nodes, and secured using IPFS hashing, making data accessible yet highly secure. Explore the future of cloud storage with us. {/* Graphics Section */} How It Works {/* File Splitting Graphic */} File Splitting Files are split into smaller chunks, ensuring secure distribution. {/* Node Distribution Graphic */} Node Distribution Chunks are distributed across multiple nodes for redundancy. {/* IPFS Hashing Graphic */} IPFS Hashing Each chunk is hashed with IPFS, providing a unique identifier. ); }; export default HomePage;
